From {{inh|en|enm|maunde}}, {{m|enm|maundie}}, from borrowed {{der|en|fro|mande}}, borrowed from {{der|en|dum|mande}}, from {{der|en|odt|*manda}}, from {{der|en|gmw-pro|*mandu}}.

